example.author: Author
example.description:
This is an example of the `!info` command. You can pass different arguments to access different chapters.
To create or edit chapters, please use my "config.js" file and use a valid embed format outlined in Discord.js documentation.
Please see [here](https://discord.js.org/#/docs/main/stable/class/MessageEmbed) or [here](https://anidiots.guide/first-bot/using-embeds-in-messages) for more details.
